### Doctor's Patient Management APIs

### 1. Get Patients Assigned to Doctor
GET http://localhost:5001/api/patients/doctor/doctor_123

### 2. Get Comprehensive Patient Data (All vitals, mental health, documents, prescriptions)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/patients/user_38LluGY5no86BOCJWUyhC5i8p6P/comprehensive

### 3. Assign Patient to Doctor (Update patient's primary_doctor_id)
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/patients/678d8a43f6e87c16e86ab1a8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primary_doctor_id": "doctor_123"
}

### 4. Get All Patients (for assignment)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/patients?limit=50

